)</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.3pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022637_image-20190224224013-47.png\" style=\"height:59px; width:117px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.25pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022637_image-20190224224013-48.png\" style=\"height:43px; width:188px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.3pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022637_image-20190224224013-49.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:241px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.25pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022637_image-20190224224013-50.png\" style=\"height:71px; width:132px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.3pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022638_image-20190224224013-51.png\" style=\"height:59px; width:122px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.25pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022638_image-20190224224013-52.png\" style=\"height:68px; width:257px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.3pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022637_image-20190224224013-53.png\" style=\"height:59px; width:236px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022637_image-20190224224013-54.png\" style=\"height:69px; width:362px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022638_image-20190224224013-55.png\" style=\"height:66px; width:136px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.25pt\">\r\n			<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551022638_image-20190224224013-56.png\" style=\"height:66px; width:195px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:239.3pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">m, n đều chẵn th&igrave; d&ugrave;ng c&ocirc;ng thức hạ bậc</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">m, n đều lẻ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; đặt t=tanx</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">m lẻ, n chẵn&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; đặt t=cosx</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">m chẵn, n lẻ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; đặt t=sinx</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">T&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n từng phần </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">C&ocirc;ng thức cần nhớ </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {u{\\rm{d}}v = uv - \\int {v{\\rm{d}}u} } \\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">C&aacute;c dạng thường gặp (P(x) l&agrave; h&agrave;m đa thức, ph&acirc;n thức biến x)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; width:479.45pt\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:162.3pt\">\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:158.7pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">u</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:158.45pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">dv</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:162.3pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\nolimits^ P\\left( x \\right).{e^{f(x)}}dx\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\nolimits^ P\\left( x \\right).sin{\\rm{ax}}dx\\)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\nolimits^ P\\left( x \\right).cos{\\rm{ax}}dx\\)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:158.7pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">P(x)</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:158.45pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({e^{f\\left( x \\right)}}\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Sinax</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">cosax</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:21.65pt; width:162.3pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {P\\left( x \\right).\\arcsin {\\rm{ax dx}}} \\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {P\\left( x \\right).\\arccos {\\rm{axdx}}} \\)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {P\\left( x \\right).\\arctan {\\rm{ax dx}}} \\)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:21.65pt; width:158.7pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">arcsin ax</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:21.65pt; width:158.45pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">P(x)</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:162.3pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {P\\left( x \\right)\\ln \\left( {f\\left( x \\right)} \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} \\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:158.7pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;ln(f(x))</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:158.45pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">P(x)</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:162.3pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {{e^{ax}}.\\sin b{\\rm{x}}} d{\\rm{x}}\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {{e^{ax}}.cosb{\\rm{x}}} d{\\rm{x}}\\)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:158.7pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({e^{ax}}\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:22.25pt; width:158.45pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;Sinbx</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Cosbx </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">(dạng n&agrave;y cần t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n từng phần 2 lần để xuất hiện t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n ban đầu)</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\">\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">T&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n x&aacute;c định </span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.2.1 Định nghĩa t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n x&aacute;c định </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định nghĩa 8.3 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh trang 207) </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">X&eacute;t h&agrave;m f(x) x&aacute;c định tr&ecirc;n [a; b] (a<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(a = {x_0} &lt; {x_1} &lt; {x_2} &lt; ... &lt; {x_{i - 1}} &lt; {x_i} &lt; ... &lt; {x_n} = b\\)</span> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">K&iacute; hiệu<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\Delta {x_i} = {x_i} - {x_{i - 1}}\\)</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;v&agrave; lấy t&ugrave;y &yacute;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\({c_i} \\in {\\rm{[}}{x_{i - 1}};{x_i}{\\rm{]}},i = \\overline {1,n} \\)</span> &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Lập tổng</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({I_n} = \\sum\\limits_1^n {f\\left( {{c_i}} \\right)\\Delta {x_i}} \\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({I_n}\\)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"> được gọi l&agrave; tổng t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n của h&agrave;m f(x) tr&ecirc;n [a; b]</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Cho số điểm chia tăng l&ecirc;n v&ocirc; hạn n</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&rarr;&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"> sao </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop {{\\rm{max}}}\\limits_{i = \\overline {1,n} } \\Delta {x_i} \\to 0\\)</span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">cho&nbsp; . Nếu trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh đ&oacute; m&agrave; <span class=\"math-tex\">\\({I_n}\\)</span> dần t&oacute;i một gi&aacute; trị x&aacute;c định I kh&ocirc;ng phụ thuộc v&agrave;o c&aacute;ch chia [a; b], c&aacute;ch chọn c<sub>i</sub> th&igrave; n&oacute;i h&agrave;m f(x) l&agrave; khả t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n [a; b] v&agrave; I gọi l&agrave; t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n x&aacute;c định của h&agrave;m f(x) tr&ecirc;n [a; b] v&agrave; k&iacute; hiệu</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(I = \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu a=b th&igrave; đặt </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:144px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:144px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx = \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^a f\\left( x \\right)dx = 0\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu a&gt;b th&igrave; đặt </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:144px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx =  - \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_b^a f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.2.2 C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh chất của t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n x&aacute;c định</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:144px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b kf\\left( x \\right)dx = k\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span></span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right) + g\\left( x \\right) - h\\left( x \\right)dx = \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx + \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b g\\left( x \\right)dx - \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b h\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span></span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx = \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_c^b f\\left( x \\right)dx + \\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^c f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span></span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu f(x)=C (C l&agrave; hằng số) th&igrave; <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b Cdx = C\\left( {b - a} \\right)\\)</span> </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu &nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f\\left( x \\right) \\le g\\left( x \\right)\\forall x \\in {\\rm{[}}a,b{\\rm{]}};a \\le b \\to \\int\\limits_a^b {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}  \\le \\int\\limits_a^b {g\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} \\)</span> </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu M, m lần lượt l&agrave; gi&aacute; trị lớn nhất v&agrave; gi&aacute; trị nhỏ nhất của h&agrave;m số f(x) tr&ecirc;n [a; b] v&agrave; &nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(a \\le b \\to m\\left( {b - a} \\right) \\le \\int\\limits_a^b {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}} \\le M\\left( {b - a} \\right)} \\)</span> </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu h&agrave;m f(x) li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n [a; b] th&igrave; tồn tại &iacute;t nhấ một điểm <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(c \\in {\\rm{[}}a;b{\\rm{]}}\\)</span> <img src=\"file:///C:/Users/LENOVO/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image004.png\" style=\"height:7px; width:7px\" />&nbsp;sao cho <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx = f\\left( c \\right)\\left( {b - a} \\right)\\)</span> </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.2.3 C&ocirc;ng thức Newton-Leibnitz</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định l&iacute; 8.1(gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 209)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu h&agrave;m f(x) li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n [a; b] v&agrave; F(x) l&agrave; một nguy&ecirc;n h&agrave;m của f(x) tr&ecirc;n đoạn [a; b] th&igrave; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx = F\\left( a \\right) - F\\left( b \\right)\\)</span></span> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Hệ quả 8.1.1(gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 210)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu h&agrave;m f(x) li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n [a; b] hoạc kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; qu&aacute; một số hữu hạn c&aacute;c điểm gi&aacute;n đoạn loại một tr&ecirc;n đoạn đ&oacute; th&igrave; h&agrave;m l&agrave; khả t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n [a; b]</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.2.4 C&aacute;c phương ph&aacute;p t&iacute;nh t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n x&aacute;c định</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\">\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">phương ph&aacute;p đổi biến số</span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định l&iacute; 8.2 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 211)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Giả sử trong t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> h&agrave;m f(x) li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n [a; b], .. l&agrave; một h&agrave;m đơn điệu, c&oacute; đạo h&agrave;m li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n [a; b] v&agrave; khi đổi biến th&igrave; <img src=\"file:///C:/Users/LENOVO/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.png\" style=\"height:7px; width:7px\" />&nbsp;f(x)dx=g(t)dt trong đ&oacute; g(t) l&agrave; một h&agrave;m li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\left( {\\varphi \\left( a \\right),\\varphi \\left( b \\right)} \\right)\\)</span> &nbsp;Khi đ&oacute; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_a^b {f(x)d{\\rm{x}} = \\int\\limits_{\\varphi \\left( a \\right)}^{\\varphi \\left( b \\right)} {g\\left( t \\right)dt} } \\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định l&iacute; 8.3 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 211)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Giả sử trong t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^b f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> h&agrave;m f(x) li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n [a; b], <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\varphi \\left( t \\right)\\)</span>l&agrave; một h&agrave;m đơn điệu, c&oacute; đạo h&agrave;m li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n[&alpha;,&beta;] ; <img src=\"file:///C:/Users/LENOVO/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.png\" style=\"height:7px; width:7px\" />&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\varphi \\left( \\alpha  \\right) = a;\\varphi \\left( \\beta  \\right) = b\\)</span> v&agrave; khi t nhận gi&aacute; trị trong [&alpha;,&beta;] th&igrave; x biến thi&ecirc;n trong [a; b]. Khi đ&oacute; bằng ph&eacute;p đổi biến ta c&oacute; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:144px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_a^b {f(x)d{\\rm{x}} = \\int\\limits_{\\varphi \\left( a \\right)}^{\\varphi \\left( b \\right)} {g\\left( t \\right)dt} } \\)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">phương ph&aacute;p t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n từng phần </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">C&ocirc;ng thức <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {u{\\rm{d}}v = uv - \\int {v{\\rm{d}}u} } \\)</span> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.3 T&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n suy rộng</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.3.1&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Trường hợp lấy khoảng t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n l&agrave; v&ocirc; hạn</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">a.Khoảng lấy t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n l&agrave; [a,+</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">)</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:168px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định nghĩa 8.4(gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 215)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Cho h&agrave;m f(x) x&aacute;c định tr&ecirc;n &nbsp;[a,+</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">khả t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n mọi đoạn [a; b] vớia&lt;b&lt;+&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">. Ta gọi v&agrave; k&iacute; hiệu t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n suy rộng của h&agrave;m f(x) tr&ecirc;n&nbsp; [a,+</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">l&agrave; giới hạn (hữu hạn hoặc v&ocirc; hạn) dưới đ&acirc;y</span><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_a^{ + \\infty } {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}  = \\mathop {\\lim }\\limits_{b \\to \\infty } \\int\\limits_a^b {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}\\)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu giới hạn tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">hữu hạn</span> th&igrave; ta n&oacute;i t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n suy rộng<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_a^{ + \\infty } {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}\\)</span>&nbsp;l&agrave; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">hội tụ</span> v&agrave; giới hạn tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; gi&aacute; trị của n&oacute;. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu giới hạn tr&ecirc;n l&agrave;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"> v&ocirc; hạn </span>hoặc <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại</span> th&igrave; ta n&oacute;i t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n suy rộng <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_a^{ + \\infty } {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}\\)</span>l&agrave; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">ph&acirc;n kỳ.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">b.Khoảng lấy t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n l&agrave; (-</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">,b]</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:54px\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_{ - \\infty }^b {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}  = \\mathop {\\lim }\\limits_{a \\to  - \\infty } \\int\\limits_a^b {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} ( - \\infty  &lt; a &lt; b)\\)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:54px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">c. Khoảng lấy t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n l&agrave;(-</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">,+</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&infin;</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:192px\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int\\limits_{ - \\infty }^{ + \\infty } {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}  = \\int\\limits_{ - \\infty }^a {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}}  + \\int\\limits_a^{ + \\infty } {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} \\)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">C&aacute;c định l&iacute; so s&aacute;nh </span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định l&iacute; 8.4 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 219)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Giả sử c&aacute;c h&agrave;m f(x), g(x) khả t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n mọi đoạn [a; b] (a</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&le;b)</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">với b lớn t&ugrave;y &yacute; v&agrave;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(0 \\le f\\left( x \\right) \\le g\\left( x \\right),\\forall x \\ge a\\)</span> . Khi đ&oacute; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } g\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span></span></span></span> &nbsp;hội tụ th&igrave;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;cũng hội tụ</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu &nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span>ph&acirc;n kỳ th&igrave; <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } g\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> cũng ph&acirc;n kỳ</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định l&iacute; 8.5(gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 219)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Giả sử c&aacute;c h&agrave;m f(x), g(x) l&agrave; c&aacute;c h&agrave;m dương, khả t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n mọi đoạn [a; b] (a</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&le;b)</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"> với b lớn t&ugrave;y &yacute; v&agrave; tỷ số giữa ch&uacute;ng c&oacute; giới hạn thỏa m&atilde;n </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(0 &lt; \\mathop {\\lim }\\limits_{x \\to  + \\infty } \\frac{{f\\left( x \\right)}}{{g\\left( x \\right)}} &lt;  + \\infty \\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Khi đ&oacute; hai t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n suy rộng <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> v&agrave; <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } g\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> đồng thời c&ugrave;ng hội tụ hoặc c&ugrave;ng ph&acirc;n kỳ.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định l&iacute; 8.6 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr220)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } \\left| {f\\left( x \\right)} \\right|dx\\)</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;hội tụ th&igrave; <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\mathop \\smallint \\limits_a^{ + \\infty } f\\left( x \\right)dx\\)</span> cũng hội tụ</span></span></span></p>', '1551022344', null, '0', '51', '1', '0', null, '0', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `lesson` VALUES ('169', 'Chương 9 : PHƯƠNG TRÌNH VI PHÂN', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551023925_c9.png\" style=\"height:500px; width:673px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551023993_c91.png\" style=\"height:779px; width:800px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024051_c92.png\" style=\"height:487px; width:800px\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Chương 9 Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.1 C&aacute;c kh&aacute;i niệm mở đầu </span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Định nghĩa 9.1 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr232)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n l&agrave; đẳng thức liện hệ giữa biến độc lập, h&agrave;m chưa biết cảu biến độc lập v&agrave; c&aacute;c đạo h&agrave;m của h&agrave;m số đ&oacute;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&rarr; phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Kh&aacute;i niệm giải một phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 232,233)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">giải một phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n l&agrave; đưa phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n đ&oacute; về một hoặc một số c&aacute;c đẳng thức tương đương, trong đ&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n c&oacute; dấu đạo h&agrave;m hoặc dấu vi ph&acirc;n</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.2 Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.2.1 Giới thiệu chung về phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Dạng biểu diễn&nbsp; F(x,y,y&#39;)=0</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dạng tổng qu&aacute;t&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{dy}}{{d{\\rm{x}}}} = f\\left( {x;y} \\right)\\)</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dạng ch&iacute;nh tắc<em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">&nbsp;y&#39;=f(x,y)</span></em><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">với f(x,y) l&agrave; h&agrave;m hai biến x&aacute;c định tr&ecirc;n miền D thuộc mặt phẳng Oxy</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 th&igrave; x, y c&oacute; vai tr&ograve; b&igrave;nh đẳng&nbsp; f(x;y)dx=g(x;y)dy</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Kết quả giải một phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Định nghĩa 9.2 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 234)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">một phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 c&oacute; thể đưa về đẳng thức tương đương dạng </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\varphi \\left( {x,C} \\right)\\)</span></strong> <span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">, trong đ&oacute; C l&agrave; hằng số tự do th&igrave; ta n&oacute;i </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\varphi \\left( {x,C} \\right)\\)</span></strong> <span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n tr&ecirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;Nếu từ nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\varphi \\left( {x,C} \\right)\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;hằng số C nhận gi&aacute; trị cụ thể n&agrave;o đ&oacute;, chẳng hạn C=C0&nbsp;th&igrave; h&agrave;m số .<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\varphi \\left( {x,{C_0}} \\right)\\)</span></strong>. &nbsp;được gọi l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n tr&ecirc;n</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">một phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 c&oacute; thể đưa về đẳng thức tương đương dạng<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\varphi \\left( {x,y,C} \\right)\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;trong đ&oacute; C l&agrave; hằng số tự do th&igrave; ta n&oacute;i <em>&nbsp;</em><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\varphi \\left( {x,y,C} \\right)\\)</span></strong> l&agrave; t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n tr&ecirc;n</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu từ t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n tổng qu&aacute;t<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\varphi \\left( {x,y,C} \\right)\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;lấy hằng số cụ thể</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">C=C0&nbsp;&nbsp;th&igrave; đẳng thức<em> </em><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> </span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\varphi \\left( {x,y,C_0} \\right)\\)</span></strong></span>được gọi l&agrave; một t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n ri&ecirc;ng của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n tr&ecirc;n</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Định l&iacute; về sự tồn tại duy nhất nghiệm</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Định l&iacute; 9.1 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 235)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cho phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 dạng ch&iacute;nh tắc&nbsp;</span>y&#39;=f(x,y)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu h&agrave;m f(x, y) li&ecirc;n tục trong miền mở D n&agrave;o đ&oacute; chứa điểm (x0,y0)&nbsp;th&igrave; tồn tại một nghiệm y=y(x) của phương tr&igrave;nh đ&oacute; sao cho y0=y(x0)&nbsp;. Nếu đạo h&agrave;m ri&ecirc;ng<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f{\'_y}\\left( {x,y} \\right)\\)</span></strong> cũng li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n D th&igrave; nghiệm đ&oacute; l&agrave; duy nhất</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.2.2 phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 biến số ph&acirc;n li</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:120px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Phương tr&igrave;nh biến số ph&acirc;n li</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng 1:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ?&prime; = ? (?). ?( ? )(2.1)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\"><strong>phương ph&aacute;p&nbsp; giải&nbsp; &nbsp; t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n 2 vế&nbsp;</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Dạng 2 :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ?(?) ?? + ?(?) ?? = 0 (2.2)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\"><strong>phương ph&aacute;p&nbsp; giải&nbsp; t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n 2 vế&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng 3 :&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(         M\\left( x \\right)N(y)d{\\rm{x}} + P(x)Q(y)dy = 0\\)</span></span><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:black\">phương ph&aacute;p&nbsp; giải</span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\">Nếu</span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(P(x)N(y)\\)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> &nbsp;&ne; 0 chia 2 vế cho<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(P(x)N(y)\\)</span></strong></span>&nbsp;&ne; 0 th&igrave; ta c&oacute; :&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{M(x)}}{{P(x)}}d{\\rm{x}} + \\frac{{Q(y)}}{{N(y)}}dy = 0\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Suy ra t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n tổng qu&aacute;t :</span> <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {\\frac{{M(x)}}{{P(x)}}d{\\rm{x}}}  + \\int {\\frac{{Q(y)}}{{N(y)}}dy}  = C\\)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">Nếu từ N(y)=0 ta c&oacute; nghiệm ? = ? th&igrave; đ&acirc;y l&agrave; nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của phương tr&igrave;nh<br />\r\nNếu từ P(x)=0 ta c&oacute; nghiệm ? = ? th&igrave; đ&acirc;y l&agrave; nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của phương tr&igrave;nh</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Dạng 4 :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;?&prime; = ?(?? + ?? + ?) (2.4)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\"><strong>Phương ph&aacute;p&nbsp; giải</strong><br />\r\nNếu ? = 0 hoặc ? = 0 ta c&oacute; dạng (2.1)<br />\r\nNếu ?? &ne; 0, đặt&nbsp; ? = ?? + ?? + ? ta c&oacute; :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;?&prime; = ??(?) + ?&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; dạng (2.1)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.2.3 Phương tr&igrave;nh đẳng cấp cấp 1</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 đẳng cấp</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(   y\' = f\\left( {x;y} \\right) = \\varphi \\left( {\\frac{y}{x}} \\right)\\)</span>(3.1)</span><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:black\">Phương ph&aacute;p&nbsp; giải</span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\">Đặt<span class=\"math-tex\">\\( u = \\frac{y}{x}\\)</span> suy ra ? = ?? n&ecirc;n ?&prime; = ? + ?&prime;?, thay v&agrave;o ta c&oacute;:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ?&prime;? = ?(?) &minus; ?</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\">Nếu ?(?) &minus; ? &ne; 0, ta c&oacute; :</span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{du}}{{\\varphi (u) - u}} = \\frac{{d{\\rm{x}}}}{x}\\)</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">Suy ra t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n tổng qu&aacute;t : </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {\\frac{{du}}{{\\varphi (u) - u}}}  = \\int {\\frac{{d{\\rm{x}}}}{x}} \\)</span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;Nếu ?(?) &minus; ? = 0 c&oacute; nghiệm ? = ? th&igrave; ? = ?? l&agrave; nghiệm<br />\r\nNếu Nếu ?(?) &minus; ? &equiv; 0 th&igrave; phương tr&igrave;nh trở th&agrave;nh</span>&nbsp;<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' = \\frac{y}{x}\\)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> &nbsp;v&agrave; n&oacute; c&oacute; nghiệm ? = ??</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\"><strong>Ch&uacute; &yacute; :</strong>Muốn kiểm tra phương tr&igrave;nh ?&prime; = ?(?, ?)<br />\r\nc&oacute; phải đẳng cấp cấp 1 kh&ocirc;ng&nbsp;ta c&oacute; thể kiểm tra ?(??,??)= ?(?, ?),&forall;? th&igrave; cho </span><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(t = \\frac{1}{x}\\)</span><span style=\"color:black\">ta c&oacute;</span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f\\left( {x;y} \\right) = f\\left( {t{\\rm{x}};ty} \\right) = f\\left( {1;\\frac{y}{x}} \\right) = \\varphi \\left( {\\frac{y}{x}} \\right)\\)</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:51px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:yellow\"><span style=\"color:black\">. </span><span style=\"color:red\">Phương tr&igrave;nh </span></span><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' = f\\left( {\\frac{{{a_1}x + {b_1}y + {c_1}}}{{{a_2}x + {b_2}y + {c_2}}}} \\right)\\)</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\">C&oacute; thể đưa về dạng biến số ph&acirc;n ly<br />\r\nTrường hợp 1 :Nếu </span><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\left| {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}} {{a_1}}&amp;{{b_1}}\\\\ {{a_2}}&amp;{{b_2}} \\end{array}} \\right| \\ne 0\\)</span><span style=\"color:black\"> th&igrave; đặt? = ? + ?;? = ? + ?&nbsp;Với ?, ? l&agrave; nghiệm của hệ </span><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} {a_1}x + {b_1}y + {c_1} = 0\\\\ {a_2}x + {b_2}y + {c_2} = 0 \\end{array} \\right.\\)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\">Khi đ&oacute;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{dz}}{{dt}} = \\frac{{dz}}{{dy}}\\frac{{dy}}{{d{\\rm{x}}}}\\frac{{d{\\rm{x}}}}{{dt}} = \\frac{{dy}}{{d{\\rm{x}}}}\\)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Thay v&agrave;o ta c&oacute; : </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(z\' = f\\left( {\\frac{{{a_1}t + {b_1}z}}{{{a_2}t + {b_2}z}}} \\right)\\)</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh đẳng cấp cấp 1.<br />\r\nTrường hợp 2 :Nếu </span><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\left| {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}} {{a_1}}&amp;{{b_1}}\\\\ {{a_2}}&amp;{{b_2}} \\end{array}} \\right| = 0\\)</span><span style=\"color:black\">th&igrave; </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{{a_1}}}{{{a_2}}} = \\frac{{{b_1}}}{{{b_2}}} = k\\)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">; ta đặt :</span><span class=\"math-tex\">\\( z = {a_2}x + {b_2}y\\)</span><span style=\"color:black\">;Ta c&oacute; : </span><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(z\' = {a_2} + {b_2}f\\left( {\\frac{{k{\\rm{z + }}{{\\rm{c}}_1}}}{{z + {c_2}}}} \\right)\\)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh biến số ph&acirc;n ly.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.2.4 Phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 1</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dạng&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">&nbsp; &nbsp;y&#39;+p(x)y=q(x)</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;(phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 1)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">&nbsp;&nbsp;y&#39;+p(x)y=0&nbsp;</span> &nbsp; &nbsp;(phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 1 thuần nhất)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">T&iacute;nh chất (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 241)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\overline y \\)</span></strong></span>&nbsp;l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất v&agrave; <span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y\\)</span></strong></span>&nbsp;l&agrave; 1 nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng n&agrave;o đ&oacute; của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất th&igrave;<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\overline y  + \\widehat y\\)</span></strong> </span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(Nguy&ecirc;n l&iacute; chồng chất nghiệm)</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y_1\\)</span></strong></span></span></span>l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">y&#39;+p(x)y=q1(x)</span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">v&agrave;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y_2\\)</span></strong></span></span></span>&nbsp;l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của &nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">y&#39;+p(x)y=q2(x)</span>&nbsp;th&igrave;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y=\\widehat y_1+\\widehat y_2\\)</span></span></em>l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">y&#39;+p(x)y=q1(x)+q2(x)</span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>*Phương ph&aacute;p biến thi&ecirc;n hằng số</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#2ecc71\">Bước 1</span> T&igrave;m nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' + p\\left( x \\right) = 0\\)</span></strong>l&agrave; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\( y = C.{e^{ - \\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }}\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#2ecc71\">Bước 2</span> (biến thi&ecirc;n hằng số)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">ở nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = C.{e^{ - \\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }}\\)</span></strong> ta coi C l&agrave; một h&agrave;m của x :&nbsp;C=C(x), nghĩa l&agrave; cho rằng <em>C&#39;&ne;0</em>). Khi đ&oacute; đạo h&agrave;m hai vế </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' = C\'.{e^{ - \\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }} - C.p\\left( x \\right).{e^{ - \\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }}\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Thay v&agrave;o phương tr&igrave;nh <span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' + p\\left( x \\right) = 0\\)</span></strong></span>&nbsp;, r&uacute;t gọn , ta được</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(     \\begin{array}{l} C\' = q\\left( x \\right).{e^{\\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }} \\Rightarrow C = \\int {q\\left( x \\right).{e^{\\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }}}  + D\\\\  \\Rightarrow y = \\left( {\\int {q\\left( x \\right).{e^{\\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }}}  + D} \\right).{e^{ - \\int {p\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}}} }} \\end{array}\\)</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(D l&agrave; hằng số t&ugrave;y &yacute;)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>*Giải phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất cấp 1 hệ số hằng bằng phương ph&aacute;p chọn (phương ph&aacute;p hệ số bất định)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh</span><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(       y\' + py = f\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\lambda  + p = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\lambda  =  - p\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Khi đ&oacute; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất l&agrave;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\overline y  = C.{e^{ - p{\\rm{x}}}}\\)</span></strong></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">T&igrave;m nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">TH1 <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f\\left( x \\right) = {P_n}\\left( x \\right).{e^{\\alpha x}}\\)</span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;th&igrave;</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#3498db\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = \\left[ \\begin{array}{l} {Q_n}\\left( x \\right).{e^{\\alpha x}}\\left( {\\alpha  \\ne  - p} \\right)\\\\ x{Q_n}\\left( x \\right).{e^{\\alpha x}}(\\alpha  =  - p) \\end{array} \\right.\\)</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">TH2&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f\\left( x \\right) = {e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{P_m}\\left( x \\right){\\rm{cosx + }}{{\\rm{Q}}_n}\\left( x \\right){\\mathop{\\rm s}\\nolimits} {\\rm{inx}}} \\right]\\)</span></span>th&igrave; <span style=\"color:#3498db\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = {e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{R_l}\\left( x \\right){\\rm{cosx + }}{{\\rm{S}}_l}\\left( x \\right){\\mathop{\\rm s}\\nolimits} {\\rm{inx}}} \\right]\\)</span></span> l=max{m,n}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Vậy nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 tuyến t&iacute;nh l&agrave;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\( y = \\overline y  + \\widehat y\\)</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Phương tr&igrave;nh Bernouli</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh </span><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' + p\\left( x \\right)y = q\\left( x \\right).{y^\\alpha }\\)</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Hướng dẫn giải </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu &alpha;=0 th&igrave; phương tr&igrave;nh Bernoulli l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 1 (đ&atilde; biết c&aacute;ch giải)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu &alpha;=1 th&igrave; ta c&oacute; l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh thuần nhất cấp 1 (đ&atilde; biết c&aacute;ch giải)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu &alpha;&lt;0 th&igrave; chia hai vế của phương tr&igrave;nh cho y<sup>&alpha;</sup> ta được&nbsp; </span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({y^{ - \\alpha }}.y\' + p\\left( x \\right){y^{1 - \\alpha }} = q\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Đặt <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(z = {y^{1 - \\alpha }}\\)</span></strong> , đưa về dạng phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh:</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(z\' + \\left( {1 - \\alpha } \\right)p\\left( x \\right)z = \\left( {1 - \\alpha } \\right)q\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu th&igrave; ngo&agrave;i nghiệm như ở 3) c&ograve;n th&ecirc;m nghiệm y=0</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.3 Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp hai </span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dạng tổng qu&aacute;t: <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(F\\left( {x,y,y\',y\'\'} \\right)\\)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dạng ch&iacute;nh tắc: y&rsquo;&rsquo;=f(x,y&rsquo;,y)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Định l&iacute; 9.5 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr249) (định l&iacute; tồn tại v&agrave; duy nhất nghiệm)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">X&eacute;t phương tr&igrave;nh y&rsquo;&rsquo;=f(x,y&rsquo;,y) . Nếu h&agrave;m f(x,y&rsquo;,y)li&ecirc;n tục trong miền mở D n&agrave;o đ&oacute; chứa điểm <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\left( {{x_0};{y_0};{y_0}\'} \\right)\\)</span></strong> th&igrave; tồn tại nghiệm y=y(x) của phương tr&igrave;nh sao cho<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\\left( {{x_0}} \\right) = {y_0};y\'\\left( {{x_0}} \\right) = {y_0}\'\\)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;Nếu <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f{\'_y}\\left( {x,y} \\right),f{\'_{y\'}}\\left( {x,y} \\right)\\)</span></strong> cũng li&ecirc;n tục tr&ecirc;n D th&igrave; nghiệm n&oacute;i tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; duy nhất</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu đưa được&nbsp; 1 phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 2 về đẳng thức tương đương dạng <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\varphi \\left( {x,{C_1},{C_2}} \\right)\\)</span></strong> trong đ&oacute; C<sub>1</sub> ,C <sub>2 </sub>l&agrave; c&aacute;c hằng số tự do th&igrave; đẳng thức n&agrave;y được&nbsp; gọi l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n đ&oacute;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Từ nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t, thay một bộ c&aacute;c gi&aacute; trị cụ thể</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({C_1} = {C_1}^0;{C_2} = {C_2}^0\\)</span></strong> ta được một h&agrave;m số x&aacute;c định l&agrave;<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\varphi \\left( {x,{C_1}^0,{C_2}^0} \\right)\\)</span></strong>&nbsp;H&agrave;m n&agrave;y được gọi l&agrave; một h&agrave;m ri&ecirc;ng </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu thay C<sub>1</sub> ,C <sub>2 </sub>bằng c&aacute;c gi&aacute; trị cụ thể </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({C_1} = {C_1}^0;{C_2} = {C_2}^0\\)</span></strong>v&agrave;o t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n tổng qu&aacute;t th&igrave; đẳng thức</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\Phi \\left( {x,y,{C_1},{C_2}} \\right)\\)</span></strong> gọi l&agrave; 1 t&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n ri&ecirc;ng</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.3.2 C&aacute;c trường hợp giảm cấp được&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Phương tr&igrave;nh giảm cấp được </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>+Khuyết y,y&rsquo;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color:red\">Phương tr&igrave;nh c&oacute; dạng&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><em><span style=\"color:red\">y&rsquo;&rsquo;=f(x)</span></em> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Hướng dẫn giải</strong>T&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n 2 lần </span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' = \\int {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}} + {C_1}}  \\Rightarrow y = \\int {\\left( {\\int {f\\left( x \\right)d{\\rm{x}} + {C_1}} } \\right)} d{\\rm{x}} + {C_2}\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>+Khuyết y&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh </span><em><span style=\"color:red\">y&rsquo;&rsquo;=f(x;y&rsquo;)</span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Hướng dẫn giải&nbsp;</strong>Đặt <em>y&rsquo;=p(x)</em> ta c&oacute;<em>y&rsquo;&rsquo;=p&rsquo;(x) </em>Khi đ&oacute; phương tr&igrave;nh về dạng</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(p\'\\left( x \\right) = f\\left( {x;p} \\right)\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 1 phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 đối với h&agrave;m p biến x.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Giả sử nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y l&agrave; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' = \\varphi \\left( {x;{C_1}} \\right)\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Giải tiếp ta được nghiệm <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\int {\\varphi (x;{C_1})d{\\rm{x}}}  + {C_2}\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>+Khuyết x&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh </span><em><span style=\"color:red\">y&rsquo;&rsquo;=f(y&rsquo;;y)</span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Hướng dẫn giải&nbsp;</strong>Kiểm tra trường hợp y=0</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Trường hợp <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y \\ne 0\\)</span></strong>&nbsp;th&igrave; đặt <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\' = p(y)\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;khi đ&oacute; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' = \\frac{{dp\\left( y \\right)}}{{d{\\rm{x}}}} = \\frac{{dp}}{{dy}}.\\frac{{dy}}{{d{\\rm{x}}}} = p\\frac{{dp}}{{dy}}\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Thay v&agrave;o phương tr&igrave;nh ta c&oacute; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(p\\frac{{dp}}{{dy}} = f(y;p)\\)</span></strong> Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 1 phương&nbsp;tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n cấp 1 đối với h&agrave;m p biến y.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Giả sử phương tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y c&oacute; nghiệm l&agrave; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(p = \\varphi \\left( {y;{C_1}} \\right)\\)</span></strong> Giải tiếp phương tr&igrave;nh <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{dy}}{{d{\\rm{x}}}} = \\varphi \\left( {y;{C_1}} \\right)\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ta được <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\frac{{dy}}{{\\varphi \\left( {y;{C_1}} \\right)}} = d{\\rm{x}}\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;. Từ đ&acirc;y ta c&oacute; <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\int {\\frac{{dy}}{{\\varphi \\left( {y;{C_1}} \\right)}}}  = x + {C_2}\\)</span></strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.3.3 phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 2</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">9.3.3.1 Dạng v&agrave; t&iacute;nh chất của phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 2</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 2 c&oacute; dạng</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + p\\left( x \\right)y\' + q\\left( x \\right)y = f\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f\\left( x \\right) \\ne 0\\)</span></strong> th&igrave; được gọi l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu f(x)=0 th&igrave; được gọi l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu p(x), q(x) khồn phụ thuộc v&agrave;o x th&igrave; n&oacute;i phương tr&igrave;nh cso hệ số hằng. Ngược lại n&oacute;i phương tr&igrave;nh c&oacute; hệ số biến thi&ecirc;n</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">T&iacute;nh chất</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất&nbsp;<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + p\\left( x \\right)y\' + q\\left( x \\right)y = f\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">bằng tổng của nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + p\\left( x \\right)y\' + q\\left( x \\right)y = 0\\)</span></strong></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">với 1 nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng n&agrave;o đ&oacute; của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(Nguy&ecirc;n l&iacute; chồng chất nghiệm)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">y<sub>1</sub> </span>l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + p\\left( x \\right)y\' + q\\left( x \\right)y = {f_1}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">v&agrave; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">y<sub>2</sub></span> l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của&nbsp;của <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + p\\left( x \\right)y\' + q\\left( x \\right)y = {f_2}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span>th&igrave;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = {y_1} + {y_2}\\)</span></strong></span> l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + p\\left( x \\right)y\' + q\\left( x \\right)y = {f_1}\\left( x \\right) + {f_2}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu y<sub>1</sub>(x); y<sub>2</sub>(x) l&agrave; hai nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất th&igrave; với mọi<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(k,h \\in R,y\\left( x \\right) = h{y_1}\\left( x \\right) + k{y_2}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong> &nbsp;cũng l&agrave; nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu y<sub>1</sub>(x); y<sub>2</sub>(x) &nbsp;l&agrave; hai nghiệm độc lập tuyến t&iacute;nh (kh&ocirc;ng tỷ lệ) của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất th&igrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất sẽ l&agrave;<strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\\left( x \\right) = {C_1}{y_1}\\left( x \\right) + {C_2}{y_2}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong> </span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 2 hệ số hằng&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + py\' + qy = f\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span><strong> </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Hướng dẫn giải</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"background-color:lime\">Bước 1</span> Giải phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({\\lambda ^2} + p\\lambda  + q = 0\\)</span></strong></span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">Bước 2</span> T&igrave;m nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\overline y \\)</span></strong> của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\overline y  = {C_1}.{e^{{\\lambda _1}x}} + {C_2}.{e^{{\\lambda _2}x}}\\)</span></strong></span> nếu&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({\\lambda _1} \\ne {\\lambda _2}\\)</span></strong></span> l&agrave; hai nghiệm ph&acirc;n biệt của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\overline y  = {C_1}.{e^{kx}} + {C_2}x.{e^{kx}}\\)</span></strong></span>nếu <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({\\lambda _1} = {\\lambda _2} = k\\)</span></strong></span>l&agrave; nghiệm k&eacute;p của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\overline y  = {e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{C_1}{\\rm{cos}}\\beta {\\rm{x + }}{C_2}{\\rm{sin}}\\beta {\\rm{x}}} \\right]\\)</span></strong></span> nếu <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\({\\lambda _{1;2}} = \\alpha  \\pm i\\beta \\)</span></strong></span> l&agrave; nghiệm phức li&ecirc;n hợp của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">Bước 3</span> T&igrave;m nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng <strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y\\)</span></strong> của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:114px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Trường hợp 1 <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f\\left( x \\right) = {e^{\\alpha x}}.{P_n}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh </span><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + py\' + qy = {e^{\\alpha x}}.{P_n}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Khi đ&oacute; th&igrave; ta x&aacute;c định nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng như sau<br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = {Q_n}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span> nếu &alpha; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave; nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = x{Q_n}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span> nếu &alpha; l&agrave; nghiệm đơn của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = {x^2}{Q_n}\\left( x \\right)\\)</span></strong></span> nếu &alpha; l&agrave; nghiệm k&eacute;p của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:114px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Trường hợp 2<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(x) = {e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{P_n}\\left( x \\right){\\rm{cos}}\\beta {\\rm{x + }}{{\\rm{P}}_m}\\left( x \\right){\\mathop{\\rm s}\\nolimits} {\\rm{in}}\\beta {\\rm{x}}} \\right]\\)</span></strong></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">Dạng phương tr&igrave;nh </span><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y\'\' + py\' + qy = {e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{P_n}\\left( x \\right){\\rm{cos}}\\beta {\\rm{x + }}{{\\rm{P}}_m}\\left( x \\right){\\mathop{\\rm s}\\nolimits} {\\rm{in}}\\beta {\\rm{x}}} \\right]\\)</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Khi đ&oacute; ta x&aacute;c định nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng như sau</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\alpha  \\pm i\\beta \\)</span></strong></span> kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave; nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng th&igrave; nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng c&oacute; thể t&igrave;m ở dạng </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = {e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{Q_l}\\left( x \\right){\\rm{cos}}\\beta {\\rm{x + }}{{\\rm{R}}_l}\\left( x \\right){\\mathop{\\rm s}\\nolimits} {\\rm{in}}\\beta {\\rm{x}}} \\right]\\)</span></strong></span> với l=max{m;n}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nếu<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\alpha  \\pm i\\beta \\)</span></strong></span> l&agrave; nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh đặc trưng th&igrave; nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng c&oacute; thể t&igrave;m ở dạng </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\widehat y = x{e^{\\alpha x}}\\left[ {{Q_l}\\left( x \\right){\\rm{cos}}\\beta {\\rm{x + }}{{\\rm{R}}_l}\\left( x \\right){\\mathop{\\rm s}\\nolimits} {\\rm{in}}\\beta {\\rm{x}}} \\right]\\)</span></strong></span> với l=max{m;n}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">Bước 4</span> nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh vi ph&acirc;n tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 2 đ&atilde; cho c&oacute; dạng <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(y = \\overline y  + \\widehat y\\)</span></strong></span> </span>&nbsp;</span></p>', '1551022883', null, '0', '51', '1', '0', null, '0', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `lesson` VALUES ('170', 'Chương 10 : PHƯƠNG TRÌNH SAI PHÂN', '<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551025343_chuong-10.png\" style=\"height:795px; width:1800px\" />Chương 10 Phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.1 Sai ph&acirc;n v&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.1.1 Lưới thời gian v&agrave; sai ph&acirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Cho điểm </span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-1.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:22px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n trục thực v&agrave; khoảng c&aacute;ch h &gt;0. Tập c&aacute;c điểm tr&ecirc;n trục thực </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-2.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:211px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">l&agrave; 1 tập hợp rời rạc, gồm c&aacute;c điểm c&aacute;ch đều nhau 1 khoảng h bắt đầu từ </span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-3.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:22px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">. Ta gọi I l&agrave; 1 lưới thời gian với bước nhảy l&agrave; h</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Sai ph&acirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Giải sử x(t) l&agrave; một h&agrave;m tr&ecirc;n lưới I , </span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-4.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:34px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Khi đ&oacute; </span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-5.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:279px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Gọi l&agrave; sai ph&acirc;n cấp 1 của h&agrave;m x(t) tại điểm t</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-6.png\" style=\"height:72px; width:726px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-7.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:359px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Tương tự</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-8.png\" style=\"height:96px; width:359px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">gọi l&agrave; sai ph&acirc;n cấp k. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">t&iacute;nh chất của sai ph&acirc;n (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 275-276)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-9.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:253px\" /></li>\r\n	<li><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-10.png\" style=\"height:37px; width:619px\" /></li>\r\n	<li><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-11.png\" style=\"height:63px; width:447px\" /></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-12.png\" style=\"height:94px; width:480px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-13.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:162px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Hệ quả</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231318-14.png\" style=\"height:94px; width:332px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.1.2 Kh&aacute;i niệm phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">*Dạng biểu diễn</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định nghĩa 10.1 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr 276)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Giả sử x(n) l&agrave; 1 h&agrave;m đối số nguy&ecirc;n chưa biết cần t&igrave;m từ đẳng thức</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-15.png\" style=\"height:53px; width:498px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Đẳng thức tr&ecirc;n được gọi l&agrave; 1 phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n với h&agrave;m cần t&igrave;m l&agrave; x(n)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">*Dạng tương đương</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-16.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:593px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu x(n) v&agrave; x(n+k) đều c&oacute; mặt th&igrave; gọi đ&oacute; l&agrave; phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n cấp k</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">*Dạng ch&iacute;nh tắc</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-17.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:669px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">*Nghiệm, nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t, nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Định nghĩa 10.2 (gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh tr277)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu đưa được 1 phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n cấp k về dạng đẳng thức tương đương dạng</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-18.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:358px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Trong đ&oacute;</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-19.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:134px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">l&agrave; c&aacute;c hằng số tự do th&igrave; (10.4) được gọi l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh sai ph&acirc;n đ&oacute;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Thay mộ bộ gi&aacute; trị hằng số cụ thể</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-20.png\" style=\"height:39px; width:171px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;v&agrave;o nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t ta được 1 nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-21.png\" style=\"height:39px; width:323px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.1.3 T&iacute;nh chất của phương tr&igrave;nh dạng tuyến t&iacute;nh</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Dạng </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-22.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:770px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-23.png\" style=\"height:73px; width:518px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Hệ số</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-24.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:23px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;phụ thuộc v&agrave;o n&rarr; hệ số biến thi&ecirc;n</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Hệ số</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024622_image-20190224231319-25.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:23px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp; kh&ocirc;ng phụ thuộc v&agrave;o n&rarr; hệ số hằng </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">*T&iacute;nh chất tập nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp k</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; nghiệm x(n)=0</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu</span><em><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></em></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-26.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:143px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;l&agrave; c&aacute;c nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất th&igrave; </span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-27.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:411px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;cũng l&agrave; nghiệm của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-28.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:247px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;l&agrave; k nghiệm độc lập tuyến t&iacute;nh của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất thfi nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất l&agrave; </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-29.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:483px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-30.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:134px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">l&agrave; hằng số t&ugrave;y &yacute;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-31.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:53px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất v&agrave; </span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-32.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:53px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;l&agrave; 1 nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng n&agrave;o đ&oacute; của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất th&igrave; </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-33.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:225px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp; l&agrave; nghiệm tổng qu&aacute;t của phương tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng thuần nhất </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">(Nguy&ecirc;n l&iacute; chồng chất nghiệm)</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-34.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:63px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của </span></span></span><br />\r\n<img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-35.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:777px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Nếu</span></span></span><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-36.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:64px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của </span></span></span><br />\r\n<img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-37.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:778px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-38.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:247px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">l&agrave; một nghiệm ri&ecirc;ng của</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-39.png\" style=\"height:72px; width:780px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.2 Phương tr&igrave;nh tuyến t&iacute;nh cấp 1</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.2.1 Phương tr&igrave;nh thuần nhất hệ số hằng</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px\"><img src=\"/public/images/course/51/lesson/1551024623_image-20190224231319-40.png\" style=\"height:36px; width:308px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px\">&nbsp;</p>', '1551024185', null, '0', '51', '1', '0', null, '0', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
