e022.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:113.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u trong nền kinh tế giản đơn</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"_x0000_i1044\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image022.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:113.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">m=<img id=\"_x0000_i1045\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image023.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:47.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Y<img id=\"_x0000_i1046\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image018.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> =m*(<img id=\"_x0000_i1047\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image015.wmz\" style=\"height:17.25pt; width:29.25pt\" /> &nbsp;)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; m: số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u(m&gt;1)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&Yacute; nghĩa: số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u cho biết sản lượng c&acirc;n bằng tăng (</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">) bao nhi&ecirc;u khi chi ti&ecirc;u tự định tăng (</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">) 1 đơn vị</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&Yacute; nghĩa m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh số nh&acirc;n: - </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">trong ngắn hạn khi nền kt chưa đạt mức sản lượng tiềm năng, chỉ cần một sự thay đổi nhỏ trong c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh phần chi ti&ecirc;u tự định sẽ l&agrave;m SLCB tăng nhanh do sự khuếch đại của số nh&acirc;n</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kt c&oacute; mức SLCB xấp xỉ mức sản lượng tiềm năng th&igrave; m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh số nh&acirc;n tỏ ra k&eacute;m hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tổng cầu v&agrave; SLCB trong nền kt đ&oacute;ng</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">AD= C + I + G</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">cầu ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng của hộ gia đ&igrave;nh</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cầu đầu tư của ch&iacute;nh phủ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">cầu chi ti&ecirc;u của ch&iacute;nh phủ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c th&agrave;nh tố trong nền kt 