t;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cho biết lượng cung tiền tăng th&ecirc;m bao nhi&ecirc;u khi tăng 1 đơn vị tiề cơ sở.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c yếu tố t&aacute;c động đến mức cung tiền danh nghĩa (MS):</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tiền cơ sở (H): NHTW quyết định :H</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt;MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tỷ lệ dự trữ thực tế ( r<img id=\"_x0000_i1045\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image007.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:8.25pt\" /> ): NHTW v&agrave; NHTM quyết định: r<img id=\"_x0000_i1046\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image007.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:8.25pt\" /> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt; MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Hệ số ưa th&iacute;ch tiền mặt (s): d&acirc;n ch&uacute;ng quyết định: s</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt;MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đồ thị:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_32\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image013.jpg\" style=\"height:174pt; rotation:-90; width:129.75pt\" /> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, Cầu tiền (L<img id=\"_x0000_i1047\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> )</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">KN: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">l&agrave; lượng tiền cần thiết cho giao dịch trong nền kt. L&agrave; lượng tiền m&agrave; mọi người muốn nắm giữ dưới dạng tiền mặt v&agrave; tiền gửi kh&ocirc;ng kỳ hạn tại c&aacute;c NHTM nhằm phục vụ giao dịch trong nền kt.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c nh&acirc;n tố t&aacute;c động:</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L&atilde;i suất: i</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;(&darr;)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt; cầu tiền</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thu&nbsp; nhập quốc d&acirc;n (Y):Y</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;(&darr;)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt;cầu tiền</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;(&darr;)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cầu về t&agrave;i sản t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh kh&aacute;c (cổ phiếu, tr&aacute;i phiếu&hellip;) &uarr;=&gt; cầu tiền&darr;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&agrave;m số v&agrave; đồ thị:</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&agrave;m cầu tiền: <strong>L<img id=\"_x0000_i1048\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> = kY-hi</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(L<img id=\"_x0000_i1049\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> ): mức cầu tiền thực tế</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">k: hệ số phản &aacute;nh sự nhạy cảm của cầu tiền so với thu nhập</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">h: hệ số phản &aacute;nh sự nhạy cảm của cầu tiền so với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đồ thị: khi cố định mức thu nhập, cầu tiền l&agrave; một h&agrave;m của l&atilde;i suất, đồ thị h&agrave;m cầu tiền l&agrave; một đường dốc xuống<strong>. Độ dốc =<img id=\"_x0000_i1050\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image015.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:17.25pt\" /> </strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_33\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image016.jpg\" style=\"height:225.75pt; rotation:-90; width:168pt\" /> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Di chuyển v&agrave; dịch chuyển đường cầu tiền:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L&atilde;i suất thay đổi =&gt;di chuyển đường cầu tiền</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thu nhập thay đổi=&gt; dịch chuyển cuả đường cầu tiền sang phải (nếu Y</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">), sang tr&aacute;i (Y</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, C&acirc;n băng thị trường tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_34\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image017.jpg\" style=\"height:336pt; rotation:-90; width:189pt\" /> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c yếu tố l&agrave;m thay đổi trạng th&aacute;i c&acirc;n bằng của thị trường tiền tệ:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi cung tiền thay đổi (giảm)= &gt;i c&acirc;n bằng thay đổi (tăng) v&agrave; ngược lại</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi thu nhập thay đổi (tăng)=&gt; l&atilde;i suất can bằng thay đổi(tăng) v&agrave; ngược lại</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi độ nhạy cảm của cầu tiền với l&atilde;i suất thay đổi tăng th&igrave; l&atilde;i suất giảm v&agrave; ngc lại</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mối quan hệ giữa thị trường tiền tệ v&agrave; thị trường tr&aacute;i phiếu</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tổng cầu về t&agrave;i sản t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh= cầu tiền + cầu tr&aacute;i phiếu=LP+DB</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tổng cung về t&agrave;i sản t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh= cung tiền+cung tr&aacute;i phiếu=MS/P+SB</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt; LP+DB= MS/P+SB </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&oacute;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">LP-MS/P=SB-DB</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi thị trường tiền tệ CB th&igrave; thị trường tr&aacute;i phiếu CB : LP=MS/P </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&oacute;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">SB=DB</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi thị trường tiền tệ dư cầu th&igrave; thị trường tr&aacute;i phiếu dư cung: LP&gt;MS/P</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&oacute;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">SB&gt;DB</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi thị trường tiền tệ dư cung th&igrave; thị trường tr&aacute;i phiếu dư cầu: LP&lt;MS/P</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&oacute;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">SB&lt;DB</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cơ chế t&aacute;c động:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kt suy tho&aacute;i, thất nghiệp cao:</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mục ti&ecirc;u:th&uacute;c đẩy tăng trưởng tạo nhiều c&ocirc;ng ăn việc l&agrave;m</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thực hiện ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ mở rộng: c&aacute;c biện ph&aacute;p để gia tăng cung tiền trong thực tế</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&ocirc;ng cụ:-mua tr&aacute;i phiếu ch&iacute;nh phủ tr&ecirc;n thị trường mở<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -</strong>giảm tỷ lệ dự trứ bắt buộc</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -giảm l&atilde;i suất chiết khấu</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt;AD tăng=&gt; tăng trưởng=&gt; giảm thất nghiệp</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kinh tế tăng trưởng n&oacute;ng, lạm ph&aacute;t cao</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mục ti&ecirc;u</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">: k&igrave;m chế tăng trưởng n&oacute;ng, hạ thấp tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thực hiện ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">tiền tệ thắt chặt:c&aacute;c biện ph&aacute;p giảm cung tiền trong thực tế</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&ocirc;ng cụ:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> :b&aacute;n tr&aacute;i phiếu ch&iacute;nh phủ tr&ecirc;n thị trường mở<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -</strong>tăng tỷ lệ dự trứ bắt buộc</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -tăng l&atilde;i suất chiết khấu</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt; AD giảm=&gt;giảm lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; giảm tăng trưởng n&oacute;ng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CHƯƠNG IV: TIỀN TỆ V&Agrave; CH&Iacute;NH S&Aacute;CH TIỀN TỆ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I, Tiền tệ c&aacute;c chức năng của tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kh&aacute;i niệm: tiền l&agrave; những t&agrave;i sản ch&iacute;nh được x&atilde; hội chấp nhận chung d&ugrave;ng l&agrave;m phương tiện thanh to&aacute;n cho c&aacute;c h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, dịch vụ.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;t&agrave;i sản t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh&rdquo; l&agrave; c&aacute;c loại giấy tờ c&oacute; gi&aacute;:-t&agrave;i sản giao dịch tiền</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -t&agrave;i sản t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh kh&aacute;c (cổ phiếu)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Chức năng của tiền:- l&agrave;m phương tiện lưu trữ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -l&agrave;m phương tiện dự trữ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -l&agrave;m phương tiện hạch to&aacute;n</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ph&acirc;n loại tiền tệ:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Theo h&igrave;nh th&aacute;i biểu hiện của tiền:- h&oacute;a tệ (tiền h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">-t&iacute;n tệ (tiền ph&aacute;p định)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -b&uacute;t tệ (tiền ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Theo t&iacute;nh thanh khoản của tiền:-tiền mặt (M<img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> )</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -tiền giao dịch (M<img id=\"_x0000_i1026\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6pt\" /> ): M<img id=\"_x0000_i1027\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6pt\" /> = M<img id=\"_x0000_i1028\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> +D</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p