if&quot;\">l&agrave; lượng tiền cần thiết cho giao dịch trong nền kt. L&agrave; lượng tiền m&agrave; mọi người muốn nắm giữ dưới dạng tiền mặt v&agrave; tiền gửi kh&ocirc;ng kỳ hạn tại c&aacute;c NHTM nhằm phục vụ giao dịch trong nền kt.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c nh&acirc;n tố t&aacute;c động:</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L&atilde;i suất: i</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;(&darr;)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt; cầu tiền</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thu&nbsp; nhập quốc d&acirc;n (Y):Y</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;(&darr;)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">=&gt;cầu tiền</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;(&darr;)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cầu về t&agrave;i sản t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh kh&aacute;c (cổ phiếu, tr&aacute;i phiếu&hellip;) &uarr;=&gt; cầu tiền&darr;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&agrave;m số v&agrave; đồ thị:</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&agrave;m cầu tiền: <strong>L<img id=\"_x0000_i1048\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> = kY-hi</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(L<img id=\"_x0000_i1049\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> ): mức cầu tiền thực tế</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">k: hệ số phản &aacute;nh sự nhạy cảm của cầu tiền so với t