-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thu nhập thay đổi=&gt; dịch chuyển cuả đường cầu tiền sang phải (nếu Y</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">), sang tr&aacute;i (Y</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, C&acirc;n băng thị trường tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_34\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image017.jpg\" style=\"height:336pt; rotation:-90; width:189pt\" /> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c yếu tố l&agrave;m thay đổi trạng th&aacute;i c&acirc;n bằng của thị trường tiền tệ:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi cung tiền thay đổi (giảm)= &gt;i c&acirc;n bằng thay đổi (tăng) v&agrave; ngược lại</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi thu nhập thay đổi (tăng)=&gt; l&atilde;i suất can bằng thay đổi(tăng) v&agrave; ngược lại</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi độ nhạy cảm của cầu tiền với l&atilde;i suất thay đổi tăng th&igrave; l&a', '1552881195', null, '0', '68', '1', '0', null, '0', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `lesson` VALUES ('732', 'chương 5', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CHƯƠNG V: M&Ocirc; H&Igrave;NH IS-LM &amp; SỰ PHỐI HỢP CSTK V&Agrave; CH&Iacute;NH S&Aacute;CH TIỀN TỆ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I, M&ocirc; h&igrave;nh IS-LM</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, c&acirc;n bằng thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a v&agrave; dịch vụ: đường IS</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">KN: đường IS biểu thị mối quan hệ giữa l&atilde;i suất (i) v&agrave; thu nhập (Y) để thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a c&acirc;n bằng: AD=Y</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&Yacute; nghĩa: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS cho biết thu nhập c&acirc;n bằng thay đổi như thế n&agrave;o khi l&atilde;i suất thay đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS dốc xuống thể hiệ khi I tăng th&igrave; Y giảm v&agrave; ngược lại</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Những điểm nằm tr&ecirc;n IS thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a cb, kh&ocirc;ng nằm tr&ecirc;n IS thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a kh&ocirc;ng CB</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Những điểm nằm dưới đường IS thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a thiếu hụt ngo&agrave;i dự kiến, nằm ngo&agrave;i th&igrave; dư thừa ngo&agrave;i dự kiến</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đồ thị:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_23\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.jpg\" style=\"height:252.75pt; left:0; margin-left:-19px; margin-top:7px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:188.15pt; z-index:251676672\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">phương tr&igrave;nh đường IS</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">: <img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:80.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ dốc</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> : -1/dm&rdquo; phụ thuộc v&agrave;o:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">-số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">-hệ số nhạy cảm của đầu tư với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Di chuyển: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">thay đổi của l&atilde;i suất=&gt; trượt dọc tr&ecirc;n IS:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_36\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image003.jpg\" style=\"height:185.35pt; left:0; margin-left:59px; margin-top:259px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:249pt; z-index:251677696\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_35\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.jpg\" style=\"height:163.5pt; rotation:180; width:219.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dịch chuyển:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> thay đổi của c&aacute;c yếu tố ngo&agrave;i l&atilde;i suất:+ CSTK mở rộng =&gt; IS sang phải</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; +CSTK thắt chặt =&gt; IS sang tr&aacute;i</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, c&acirc;n bằng thị trường tiền tệ - đường LM</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">KN: đường LM biểu thị mối quan hệ giữa l&atilde;i suất (i) v&agrave; thu nhập (Y) tại đ&oacute; thị trường tiền tệ c&acirc;n bằng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&Yacute; nghĩa:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;<img id=\"Picture_x0020_37\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image005.jpg\" style=\"height:324.75pt; rotation:-90; width:182.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Phương tr&igrave;nh&nbsp; đường LM: MS/P=L<img id=\"_x0000_i1026\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image006.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&oacute;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> <img id=\"_x0000_i1027\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image007.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:83.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ dốc đường LM: (=k/h) phụ thuộc v&agrave;o:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ nhạy cảm của cầu tiền với thu nhập (k)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ nhạy cảm của cầu tiền với l&atilde;i suất (h)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Di chuyển LM: &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_38\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image008.jpg\" style=\"height:267pt; rotation:-90; width:198.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dịch chuyển LM:&nbsp; MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (CSTK mở rộng)=&gt;LM dịch chuyển xuống dưới</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (CSTK thắt chặt)=&gt; LM dịch chuyển l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_39\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image009.jpg\" style=\"height:263.25pt; rotation:-90; width:195.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, M&ocirc; h&igrave;nh IS-LM: c&acirc;n bằng tr&ecirc;n thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a v&agrave; thị trường tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_40\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image010.jpg\" style=\"height:195.95pt; position:absolute; width:263.25pt; z-index:251678720\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">tại bất kỳ điểm n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c điểm E, sẽ c&oacute; &iacute;t nhất một thị trường kh&ocirc;ng c&acirc;n bằng.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">x&aacute;c định l&atilde;i suất v&agrave; SLCB chung&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (i<img id=\"_x0000_i1028\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image011.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> &nbsp;v&agrave; Y<img id=\"_x0000_i1029\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image011.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> ): thỏa m&atilde;n phương tr&igrave;nh:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img id=\"_x0000_i1030\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:64.5pt; width:83.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">II, </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;<strong>T&aacute;c động của CSTK v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ tr&ecirc;n m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh IS-LM</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, T&aacute;c động CSTK lỏng (mở rộng)<br />\r\n<img id=\"Picture_x0020_42\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image013.jpg\" style=\"height:256.5pt; rotation:90; width:193.5pt\" /><br />\r\nTrường hợp đặc biệt: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTK lỏng =&gt; i kh&ocirc;ng đổi, Y tăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTK lỏng =&gt; i tăng, Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTK lỏng=&gt; i, Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTK lỏng =&gt; i v&agrave; Y c&ugrave;ng tăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nhận x&eacute;t: -khi đường LM c&agrave;ng thoải (cầu tiền k&eacute;m nhạy cảm với thu nhập, nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất.): =&gt; CSTK c&agrave;ng hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS c&agrave;ng thoải ( đầu tư c&agrave;ng&nbsp; nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất)=&gt; CSTK c&agrave;ng k&eacute;m hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, T&aacute;c động CSTK thắt chặt</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTK thắt chặt =&gt;i giảm, Y giảm</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_43\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.jpg\" style=\"height:199.1pt; position:absolute; width:265.5pt; z-index:251680768\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">nhận x&eacute;t:( như tr&ecirc;n)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, T&aacute;c động của ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ lỏng:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_47\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image015.jpg\" style=\"height:200.45pt; position:absolute; width:149.25pt; z-index:251681792\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trường hợp đặc biệt:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt; i kh&ocirc;ng đổi, Ytăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt;i giảm, Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt; i giảm, Y tăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt; i v&agrave; Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4,&nbsp; T&aacute;c động của ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ chặt</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTK chặt =&gt; i tăng, Y giảm<br />\r\n<strong><em>Nhận x&eacute;t t&aacute;c động của CSTT :</em></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTT c&agrave;ng hiệu quả khi:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường LM c&agrave;ng thoải</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_48\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image016.jpg\" style=\"height:168.75pt; left:0; margin-left:-26px; margin-top:-107px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:225pt; z-index:251682816\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">cầu tiền k&eacute;m nhạy cảm với thu nhập</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">cầu tiền c&agrave;ng nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS c&agrave;ng thoải</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đầu tư c&agrave;ng nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u c&agrave;ng lớn</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTT c&agrave;ng k&eacute;m hiệu quả khi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường LM c&agrave;ng dốc</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS c&agrave;ng dốc</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III, Kết hợp CSTK v&agrave; Tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, CSTK lỏng v&agrave; CSTT lỏng </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kt c&oacute; mức tổng cầu qu&aacute; thấp: sử dụng kết hợp CSTK lỏng v&agrave; CSTT lỏng sẽ l&agrave;m tổng cầu v&aacute; sản lượng tăng mạnh</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2,CSTK chặt v&agrave; CSTT chặt </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kt c&oacute; mức tổng cầu qu&aacute; cao: kết hợp dử dụng CSTK chặt v&agrave; CSTT chặt sẽ l&agrave; giảm mạnh tổng cầu v&agrave; kiểm so&aacute;t lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, CSTK lỏng v&agrave; CSTT chặt</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gi&uacute;p ổn định sản lượng thay đổi cơ cấu đầu tư: tăng đầu tư c&ocirc;ng, giảm ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; đầu tư tư nh&acirc;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4, CSTK chặt v&agrave; CSTT lỏng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gi&uacute;p ổn định sản lượng, thay đổi cơ cấu đầu tư: giảm đầu tư c&ocirc;ng, tăng ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; đầu tư tư nh&acirc;n</span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CHƯƠNG V: M&Ocirc; H&Igrave;NH IS-LM &amp; SỰ PHỐI HỢP CSTK V&Agrave; CH&Iacute;NH S&Aacute;CH TIỀN TỆ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I, M&ocirc; h&igrave;nh IS-LM</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, c&acirc;n bằng thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a v&agrave; dịch vụ: đường IS</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">KN: đường IS biểu thị mối quan hệ giữa l&atilde;i suất (i) v&agrave; thu nhập (Y) để thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a c&acirc;n bằng: AD=Y</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&Yacute; nghĩa: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS cho biết thu nhập c&acirc;n bằng thay đổi như thế n&agrave;o khi l&atilde;i suất thay đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS dốc xuống thể hiệ khi I tăng th&igrave; Y giảm v&agrave; ngược lại</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Những điểm nằm tr&ecirc;n IS thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a cb, kh&ocirc;ng nằm tr&ecirc;n IS thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a kh&ocirc;ng CB</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Những điểm nằm dưới đường IS thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a thiếu hụt ngo&agrave;i dự kiến, nằm ngo&agrave;i th&igrave; dư thừa ngo&agrave;i dự kiến</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đồ thị:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_23\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.jpg\" style=\"height:252.75pt; left:0; margin-left:-19px; margin-top:7px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:188.15pt; z-index:251676672\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">phương tr&igrave;nh đường IS</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">: <img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:80.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ dốc</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> : -1/dm&rdquo; phụ thuộc v&agrave;o:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">-số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">-hệ số nhạy cảm của đầu tư với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Di chuyển: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">thay đổi của l&atilde;i suất=&gt; trượt dọc tr&ecirc;n IS:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_36\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image003.jpg\" style=\"height:185.35pt; left:0; margin-left:59px; margin-top:259px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:249pt; z-index:251677696\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_35\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.jpg\" style=\"height:163.5pt; rotation:180; width:219.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dịch chuyển:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> thay đổi của c&aacute;c yếu tố ngo&agrave;i l&atilde;i suất:+ CSTK mở rộng =&gt; IS sang phải</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; +CSTK thắt chặt =&gt; IS sang tr&aacute;i</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, c&acirc;n bằng thị trường tiền tệ - đường LM</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">KN: đường LM biểu thị mối quan hệ giữa l&atilde;i suất (i) v&agrave; thu nhập (Y) tại đ&oacute; thị trường tiền tệ c&acirc;n bằng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&Yacute; nghĩa:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;<img id=\"Picture_x0020_37\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image005.jpg\" style=\"height:324.75pt; rotation:-90; width:182.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Phương tr&igrave;nh&nbsp; đường LM: MS/P=L<img id=\"_x0000_i1026\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image006.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&oacute;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> <img id=\"_x0000_i1027\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image007.wmz\" style=\"height:30.75pt; width:83.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ dốc đường LM: (=k/h) phụ thuộc v&agrave;o:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ nhạy cảm của cầu tiền với thu nhập (k)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Độ nhạy cảm của cầu tiền với l&atilde;i suất (h)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Di chuyển LM: &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_38\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image008.jpg\" style=\"height:267pt; rotation:-90; width:198.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dịch chuyển LM:&nbsp; MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (CSTK mở rộng)=&gt;LM dịch chuyển xuống dưới</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MS</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&darr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (CSTK thắt chặt)=&gt; LM dịch chuyển l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_39\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image009.jpg\" style=\"height:263.25pt; rotation:-90; width:195.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, M&ocirc; h&igrave;nh IS-LM: c&acirc;n bằng tr&ecirc;n thị trường h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a v&agrave; thị trường tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_40\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image010.jpg\" style=\"height:195.95pt; position:absolute; width:263.25pt; z-index:251678720\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">tại bất kỳ điểm n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c điểm E, sẽ c&oacute; &iacute;t nhất một thị trường kh&ocirc;ng c&acirc;n bằng.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">x&aacute;c định l&atilde;i suất v&agrave; SLCB chung&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (i<img id=\"_x0000_i1028\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image011.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> &nbsp;v&agrave; Y<img id=\"_x0000_i1029\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image011.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> ): thỏa m&atilde;n phương tr&igrave;nh:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img id=\"_x0000_i1030\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:64.5pt; width:83.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">II, </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;<strong>T&aacute;c động của CSTK v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ tr&ecirc;n m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh IS-LM</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, T&aacute;c động CSTK lỏng (mở rộng)<br />\r\n	<img id=\"Picture_x0020_42\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image013.jpg\" style=\"height:256.5pt; rotation:90; width:193.5pt\" /><br />\r\n	Trường hợp đặc biệt: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTK lỏng =&gt; i kh&ocirc;ng đổi, Y tăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTK lỏng =&gt; i tăng, Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTK lỏng=&gt; i, Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTK lỏng =&gt; i v&agrave; Y c&ugrave;ng tăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nhận x&eacute;t: -khi đường LM c&agrave;ng thoải (cầu tiền k&eacute;m nhạy cảm với thu nhập, nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất.): =&gt; CSTK c&agrave;ng hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS c&agrave;ng thoải ( đầu tư c&agrave;ng&nbsp; nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất)=&gt; CSTK c&agrave;ng k&eacute;m hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, T&aacute;c động CSTK thắt chặt</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTK thắt chặt =&gt;i giảm, Y giảm</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_43\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image014.jpg\" style=\"height:199.1pt; position:absolute; width:265.5pt; z-index:251680768\" /><br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">nhận x&eacute;t:( như tr&ecirc;n)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, T&aacute;c động của ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ lỏng:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_47\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image015.jpg\" style=\"height:200.45pt; position:absolute; width:149.25pt; z-index:251681792\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trường hợp đặc biệt:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt; i kh&ocirc;ng đổi, Ytăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi IS thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt;i giảm, Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM nằm ngang th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt; i giảm, Y tăng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi LM thẳng đứng th&igrave; CSTT lỏng=&gt; i v&agrave; Y kh&ocirc;ng đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4,&nbsp; T&aacute;c động của ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền tệ chặt</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTK chặt =&gt; i tăng, Y giảm<br />\r\n	<strong><em>Nhận x&eacute;t t&aacute;c động của CSTT :</em></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTT c&agrave;ng hiệu quả khi:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường LM c&agrave;ng thoải</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_48\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image016.jpg\" style=\"height:168.75pt; left:0; margin-left:-26px; margin-top:-107px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:225pt; z-index:251682816\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">cầu tiền k&eacute;m nhạy cảm với thu nhập</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">cầu tiền c&agrave;ng nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS c&agrave;ng thoải</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đầu tư c&agrave;ng nhạy cảm với l&atilde;i suất</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Số nh&acirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u c&agrave;ng lớn</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CSTT c&agrave;ng k&eacute;m hiệu quả khi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường LM c&agrave;ng dốc</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đường IS c&agrave;ng dốc</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III, Kết hợp CSTK v&agrave; Tiền tệ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, CSTK lỏng v&agrave; CSTT lỏng </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kt c&oacute; mức tổng cầu qu&aacute; thấp: sử dụng kết hợp CSTK lỏng v&agrave; CSTT lỏng sẽ l&agrave;m tổng cầu v&aacute; sản lượng tăng mạnh</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2,CSTK chặt v&agrave; CSTT chặt </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi nền kt c&oacute; mức tổng cầu qu&aacute; cao: kết hợp dử dụng CSTK chặt v&agrave; CSTT chặt sẽ l&agrave; giảm mạnh tổng cầu v&agrave; kiểm so&aacute;t lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, CSTK lỏng v&agrave; CSTT chặt</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gi&uacute;p ổn định sản lượng thay đổi cơ cấu đầu tư: tăng đầu tư c&ocirc;ng, giảm ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; đầu tư tư nh&acirc;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4, CSTK chặt v&agrave; CSTT lỏng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gi&uacute;p ổn định sản lượng, thay đổi cơ cấu đầu tư: giảm đầu tư c&ocirc;ng, tăng ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; đầu tư tư nh&acirc;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '1552881277', null, '0', '68', '1', '0', null, '0', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `lesson` VALUES ('733', 'chương 6', '<p>v</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CHƯƠNG VI: LẠM PH&Aacute;T V&Agrave; THẤT NGHIỆP</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I, Lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1,Kn: l&agrave; sự tăng l&ecirc;n li&ecirc;n tục của mức gi&aacute; chung theo thời gian</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đo lường lạm ph&aacute;t: <img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.wmz\" style=\"height:35.25pt; width:131.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trong đ&oacute;: g<img id=\"_x0000_i1026\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> &nbsp;l&agrave; tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t thời kỳ (t)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I<img id=\"_x0000_i1027\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> chỉ số gi&aacute; thời kỳ (t)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I<img id=\"_x0000_i1028\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image003.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:15pt\" /> &nbsp;chỉ số gi&aacute; thời kỳ trước</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&oacute; 3 loại : lạm ph&aacute;t vừa phải, lạm ph&aacute;t phi m&atilde;, si&ecirc;u lạm ph&aacute;t.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n của lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a, lạm ph&aacute;t do cầu k&eacute;o</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_44\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.jpg\" style=\"height:210.35pt; left:0; margin-left:356px; margin-top:-26px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:168pt; z-index:251683840\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n: do sự gia tăng nhanh của tổng cầu khi sản lượng đ&atilde; đạt được hoặc vượt mức sản lượng tiền năng </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bản chất: chi ti&ecirc;u qu&aacute; nhiều tiền để mua một lượng cung hạn chế v&egrave; h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a v&agrave; dịch vụ trong điều kiện thị trường đ&atilde; đạt c&acirc;n bằng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">b, lạm ph&aacute;t do chi ph&iacute; đẩy</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_45\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image005.jpg\" style=\"height:221.35pt; margin-left:426px; margin-top:-92px; position:absolute; width:164.75pt; z-index:251684864\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n: lạm ph&aacute;t xảy ra do gi&aacute; cả của c&aacute;c yếu tố đầu v&agrave;o tăng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đầu v&agrave;o cơ bản: tiền c&ocirc;ng, tiền lương, nguy&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n vật liệu</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Chi ph&iacute; kh&aacute;c: thuế gi&aacute;n thu</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gi&aacute; cả sản phẩm trung gian</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lạm ph&aacute;t chi ph&iacute; đẩy c&ograve;n gọi l&agrave; &ldquo; lạm ph&aacute;t đ&igrave;nh trệ&rdquo;,xảy ra ngay cả khi Y=Y*</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; l&atilde;i suất: l&atilde;i suất thực tế = l&atilde;i suất danh nghĩa-tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; r = i - g<img id=\"_x0000_i1029\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image006.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3,&nbsp; T&aacute;c động của lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lạm ph&aacute;t g&acirc;y ra c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng cần thiết đối với nền kinh tế: chi ph&iacute; m&ograve;n giầy; chi ph&iacute; thực đơn</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lạm ph&aacute;t cao + gi&aacute; cả tăng kh&ocirc;ng đều giữa c&aacute;c nh&oacute;m h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, dịch vụ; tăng gi&aacute; cả v&agrave; tiền lương kh&ocirc;ng xảy ra đồng thời sẽ dẫn đến:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ph&acirc;n phối thu nhập ngẫu nhi&ecirc;n =&gt; giảm động lực ph&aacute;t triển kt</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Biến dạng cơ cấu sản xuất v&agrave; việc l&agrave;m =&gt;giảm hiệu quả ph&aacute;t triển kinh tế</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mất ổn định kinh tế, ch&iacute;nh trị</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4, biện ph&aacute;p kiềm chế lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Giảm lạm ph&aacute;t từ ph&iacute;a cầu: sử dụng CSTK thắt chặt, CSTT thắt chặt v&agrave; c&aacute;c biện ph&aacute;p kiểm so&aacute;t trực tiếp (kiểm so&aacute;t gi&aacute;, l&atilde;i suất,..)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Giảm lạm ph&aacute;t từ ph&iacute;a cung:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dử dụng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch l&agrave;m giảm chi ph&iacute; sản xuất, n&acirc;ng cao năng lực sản xuất (khuyến kh&iacute;ch &aacute;p dụng thiết bị kỹ thuật, đ&agrave;o tạo n&acirc;ng cao chất lượng lao động,..)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">II, Thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, Kn: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">những người trong LLLXH kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; việc l&agrave;m v&agrave; đang t&iacute;ch cực t&igrave;m kiếm việc l&agrave;m</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"_x0000_i1030\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image007.wmz\" style=\"height:15.75pt; width:38.25pt\" /> </span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">số người thất nghiệp</span></span></em><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">LLLĐXH</span></span></em><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&times;100</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image008.png\" style=\"height:23.25pt; width:119.25pt\" /> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">%</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp; <strong>2, </strong>Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n thất nghiệp</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Người lao động cần c&oacute; thời gian để t&igrave;m được việc l&agrave;m ph&ugrave; hợp nhất đối với họ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do sự thay đổi nhu cầu lao động giữa c&aacute;c doanh ngiệp</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do sự thay đổi nhu cầu việc l&agrave;m của người lao động</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; những người mới tham gia hoặc t&aacute;i nhập vafp LLLĐ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Sự vượt qu&aacute; cung so với cầu lao động</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do luật tiền lương tối thiểu, t&aacute;c động của c&aacute;c tổ chức c&ocirc;ng đo&agrave;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do cơ cấu kinh tế thay đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do t&iacute;nh chu kỳ của nền kt</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, t&aacute;c động của thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G&oacute;c độ kinh tế:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nền kt hoạt động k&eacute;m hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute; nh&acirc;n, gia đ&igrave;nh người thất nghiệp chịu nhiều thiệt th&ograve;i v&igrave; mất thu nhập, kỹ năng x&oacute;i m&ograve;n, t&acirc;m l&yacute; kh&ocirc;ng tốt</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G&oacute;c</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> độ x&atilde; hội: dễ nảy sinh nhiều tệ nạn XH, ch&iacute;nh phủ phải chi nhiều tiền trọe cấp thất nghiệp</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G&oacute;c độ </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ch&iacute;nh trị: người lao động giảm l&ograve;ng tin v&agrave;o ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh phủ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4, biện ph&aacute;p giảm thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đối với thất nghiệp tự nhi&ecirc;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tạo điều kiện để thị trường lao động hoạt động hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tăng cường c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c đ&agrave;o tạo</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đối với thất nghiệp do thiếu cầu:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thực hiện ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch th&uacute;c đẩy tăng trưởng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cải c&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền lương</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III, Mối quan hệ giữa lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, Mối quan hệ trong ngắn hạn</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a, đường philips ban đầu</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp c&oacute; quan hệ nghịch =&gt; c&oacute; thể đ&aacute;nh đổi lạm ph&aacute;t cao hơn để lấy mức thất nghiệp thấp hơn</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_50\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image009.jpg\" style=\