ns-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&yacute; nghĩa đường phillips: l&agrave; cơ sở cho những người l&agrave;m ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch lựa chọn ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch vĩ m&ocirc;. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_52\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image011.jpg\" style=\"height:179.55pt; margin-left:251px; margin-top:4px; position:absolute; width:164.25pt; z-index:-251629568\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">c, đường phillips mở rộng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">gp = gp<img id=\"_x0000_i1031\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> &nbsp;- </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&epsilon;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(u-u*)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">gp<img id=\"_x0000_i1032\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> : tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t dự kiến</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">khi u=u* th&igrave; gp = gp<img id=\"_x0000_i1033\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">khi u &gt; u* th&igrave; gp &lt; gp<img id=\"_x0000_i1034\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">khi u&lt;u* th&igrave; gp&gt; gp<img id=\"_x0000_i1035\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_55\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image013.jpg\" style=\"height:180.05pt; left:0; margin-left:250px; margin-top:12px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:153.55pt; z-index:-251628544\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, mối quan hệ trong d&agrave;i hạn</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trong d&agrave;i hạn gp = gp<img id=\"_x0000_i1036\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image012.wmz\" style=\"height:18pt; width:6.75pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">0= - </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&epsilon;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(u-u*) =&gt; u= u*</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kết lận về mối quan hệ giữa lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trong ngắn hạn: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">nền kt vận động theo c&aacute;c đường PC. C&oacute; sự đ&aacute;nh đổi tạm thời giữa lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp trong thời gian nền kt tự điều chỉnh bởi c&aacute;c cơn sốt cầu, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; sự đ&aacute;nh đổi bởi c&aacute;c cơn sốt cung</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trong d&agrave;i hạn:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại mối quan hệ lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CHƯƠNG VI: LẠM PH&Aacute;T V&Agrave; THẤT NGHIỆP</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I, Lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1,Kn: l&agrave; sự tăng l&ecirc;n li&ecirc;n tục của mức gi&aacute; chung theo thời gian</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đo lường lạm ph&aacute;t: <img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.wmz\" style=\"height:35.25pt; width:131.25pt\" /> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trong đ&oacute;: g<img id=\"_x0000_i1026\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> &nbsp;l&agrave; tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t thời kỳ (t)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I<img id=\"_x0000_i1027\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image002.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> chỉ số gi&aacute; thời kỳ (t)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I<img id=\"_x0000_i1028\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image003.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:15pt\" /> &nbsp;chỉ số gi&aacute; thời kỳ trước</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&oacute; 3 loại : lạm ph&aacute;t vừa phải, lạm ph&aacute;t phi m&atilde;, si&ecirc;u lạm ph&aacute;t.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2, Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n của lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a, lạm ph&aacute;t do cầu k&eacute;o</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_44\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.jpg\" style=\"height:210.35pt; left:0; margin-left:356px; margin-top:-26px; position:absolute; text-align:left; width:168pt; z-index:251683840\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n: do sự gia tăng nhanh của tổng cầu khi sản lượng đ&atilde; đạt được hoặc vượt mức sản lượng tiền năng </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bản chất: chi ti&ecirc;u qu&aacute; nhiều tiền để mua một lượng cung hạn chế v&egrave; h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a v&agrave; dịch vụ trong điều kiện thị trường đ&atilde; đạt c&acirc;n bằng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">b, lạm ph&aacute;t do chi ph&iacute; đẩy</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_45\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image005.jpg\" style=\"height:221.35pt; margin-left:426px; margin-top:-92px; position:absolute; width:164.75pt; z-index:251684864\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n: lạm ph&aacute;t xảy ra do gi&aacute; cả của c&aacute;c yếu tố đầu v&agrave;o tăng</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đầu v&agrave;o cơ bản: tiền c&ocirc;ng, tiền lương, nguy&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n vật liệu</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Chi ph&iacute; kh&aacute;c: thuế gi&aacute;n thu</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gi&aacute; cả sản phẩm trung gian</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lạm ph&aacute;t chi ph&iacute; đẩy c&ograve;n gọi l&agrave; &ldquo; lạm ph&aacute;t đ&igrave;nh trệ&rdquo;,xảy ra ngay cả khi Y=Y*</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; l&atilde;i suất: l&atilde;i suất thực tế = l&atilde;i suất danh nghĩa-tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; r = i - g<img id=\"_x0000_i1029\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image006.wmz\" style=\"height:18.75pt; width:9pt\" /> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3,&nbsp; T&aacute;c động của lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lạm ph&aacute;t g&acirc;y ra c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng cần thiết đối với nền kinh tế: chi ph&iacute; m&ograve;n giầy; chi ph&iacute; thực đơn</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lạm ph&aacute;t cao + gi&aacute; cả tăng kh&ocirc;ng đều giữa c&aacute;c nh&oacute;m h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, dịch vụ; tăng gi&aacute; cả v&agrave; tiền lương kh&ocirc;ng xảy ra đồng thời sẽ dẫn đến:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ph&acirc;n phối thu nhập ngẫu nhi&ecirc;n =&gt; giảm động lực ph&aacute;t triển kt</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Biến dạng cơ cấu sản xuất v&agrave; việc l&agrave;m =&gt;giảm hiệu quả ph&aacute;t triển kinh tế</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mất ổn định kinh tế, ch&iacute;nh trị</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4, biện ph&aacute;p kiềm chế lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Giảm lạm ph&aacute;t từ ph&iacute;a cầu: sử dụng CSTK thắt chặt, CSTT thắt chặt v&agrave; c&aacute;c biện ph&aacute;p kiểm so&aacute;t trực tiếp (kiểm so&aacute;t gi&aacute;, l&atilde;i suất,..)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Giảm lạm ph&aacute;t từ ph&iacute;a cung:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dử dụng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch l&agrave;m giảm chi ph&iacute; sản xuất, n&acirc;ng cao năng lực sản xuất (khuyến kh&iacute;ch &aacute;p dụng thiết bị kỹ thuật, đ&agrave;o tạo n&acirc;ng cao chất lượng lao động,..)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">II, Thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, Kn: </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">những người trong LLLXH kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; việc l&agrave;m v&agrave; đang t&iacute;ch cực t&igrave;m kiếm việc l&agrave;m</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><img id=\"_x0000_i1030\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image007.wmz\" style=\"height:15.75pt; width:38.25pt\" /> </span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">số người thất nghiệp</span></span></em><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">LLLĐXH</span></span></em><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&times;100</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image008.png\" style=\"height:23.25pt; width:119.25pt\" /> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">%</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp; <strong>2, </strong>Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n thất nghiệp</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Người lao động cần c&oacute; thời gian để t&igrave;m được việc l&agrave;m ph&ugrave; hợp nhất đối với họ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do sự thay đổi nhu cầu lao động giữa c&aacute;c doanh ngiệp</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do sự thay đổi nhu cầu việc l&agrave;m của người lao động</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; những người mới tham gia hoặc t&aacute;i nhập vafp LLLĐ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Sự vượt qu&aacute; cung so với cầu lao động</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do luật tiền lương tối thiểu, t&aacute;c động của c&aacute;c tổ chức c&ocirc;ng đo&agrave;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do cơ cấu kinh tế thay đổi</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Do t&iacute;nh chu kỳ của nền kt</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3, t&aacute;c động của thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G&oacute;c độ kinh tế:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nền kt hoạt động k&eacute;m hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute; nh&acirc;n, gia đ&igrave;nh người thất nghiệp chịu nhiều thiệt th&ograve;i v&igrave; mất thu nhập, kỹ năng x&oacute;i m&ograve;n, t&acirc;m l&yacute; kh&ocirc;ng tốt</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G&oacute;c</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> độ x&atilde; hội: dễ nảy sinh nhiều tệ nạn XH, ch&iacute;nh phủ phải chi nhiều tiền trọe cấp thất nghiệp</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">G&oacute;c độ </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ch&iacute;nh trị: người lao động giảm l&ograve;ng tin v&agrave;o ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh phủ</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4, biện ph&aacute;p giảm thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đối với thất nghiệp tự nhi&ecirc;n</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tạo điều kiện để thị trường lao động hoạt động hiệu quả</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tăng cường c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c đ&agrave;o tạo</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đối với thất nghiệp do thiếu cầu:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thực hiện ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch th&uacute;c đẩy tăng trưởng</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cải c&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tiền lương</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III, Mối quan hệ giữa lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1, Mối quan hệ trong ngắn hạn</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a, đường philips ban đầu</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t v&agrave; thất nghiệp c&oacute; quan hệ nghịch =&gt; c&oacute; thể đ&aacute;nh đổi lạm ph&aacute;t cao hơn để lấy mức thất nghiệp thấp hơn</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_50\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image009.jpg\" style=\"height:189.65pt; margin-left:16px; margin-top:-24px; position:absolute; width:138.7pt; z-index:251685888\" /> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img id=\"Picture_x0020_51\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image010.jpg\" style=\"height:166.7pt; margin-left:357px; margin-top:-6px; position:absolute; width:165.25pt; z-index:-251627520\" /> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">b, Đường phillips ho&agrave;n chỉnh</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">gp= -</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&epsilon;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(u &ndash; u*)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">gp: tỷ lệ lạm ph&aacute;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">u: tỷ lệ thất nghiệp thực tế</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span styl